description: Submission of reserved matters in respect of siting, design, external appearance and landscaping pursuant to conditions 01, 02, 03 & 04 and details of phasing of construction works, means of enclosure, parking and turning facilities, refuse storage, cycle parking, Lifetime Homes standards and accessibility for wheelchair users pursuant to conditions 05, 06, 07, 13, 25, 32 & 33 of outline approval under Ref:TP/04/2623/VAR1 for redevelopment of plots 4 & 5 for 330 residential units, comprising 47 x 2-storey and 13 x 3-storey houses and 270 apartments in 3 and 4-storey blocks, with associated car parking and vehicular access to Kinetic Crescent and Ordnance Road.
